content:
Display FlexCard Data in a Tabular Structure

You can display a tabular structure of the data fetched from a data source on a FlexCard. For example, display Account Cases as a sortable table.

Add a Datatable to a FlexCard
Add the Datatable element in FlexCard Designer.
FlexCards Datatable Properties
Datatable element properties are configurable in the Property Panel when you select a Datatable element in the FlexCard Designer. With the Datatable element, display a tabular structure of the data fetched from a data source.

Download a Sample Datatable DataPack
Download a sample Datatable DataPack to import into your org. A Datatable element lets you display a tabular structure of the data fetched from a data source on a FlexCard.
title: Displaying Data in Tabular Structure with OmniStudio
